<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>API Key Rotation Required</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #FFA000;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #fff;
    }
    .warning {
      background-color: #FFF3E0;
      border: 1px solid #FFE0B2;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .key-info {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #FFA000;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>API Key Rotation Required</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="warning">
        <strong>Action Required:</strong>
        <p>Your API key will expire in {{daysUntilExpiry}} days. Please update your integration to use the new API key.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="key-info">
        <h3>Current API Key:</h3>
        <p><code>{{currentKey}}</code></p>
        <p>Expires: {{expiryDate}}</p>
        
        <h3>New API Key:</h3>
        <p><code>{{newKey}}</code></p>
      </div>
      
      <h3>Next Steps:</h3>
      <ol>
        <li>Update your integration to use the new API key</li>
        <li>Test your integration with the new key</li>
        <li>Verify all systems are working correctly</li>
        <li>The old key will be automatically deactivated on the expiry date</li>
      </ol>
      
      <a href="https://dashboard.pipaymentgateway.com/api-keys" class="button">
        Manage API Keys
      </a>
      
      <p>For security reasons, this new API key will only be shown once. Please store it securely.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Â© 2025 Pi Payment Gateway. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>